{"tid":2438815,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"范徐麗泰：如果犧牲港人自由，則香港社會繁榮安定目的，必難達到","createTime":"2021-03-08T19:12:32.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-09T00:51:08.000Z","uid":261647,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"bf7fb07a12d50ab6f0ea957e1417bcd0ab1288b8","tid":2438815,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T19:12:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/recall.hk/posts/2906546033000769\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Frecall.hk%2Fposts%2F2906546033000769&d=5FApYPwYYRZ83iNn2U1Rv7is81FSeaDeH2Oz4vdBzj8%3D&h=a45b762a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/recall.hk/posts/2906546033000769</a><br />\n<br />\n作者：世代懺悔錄：香港前途考古札記<br />\n<br />\n#范徐麗泰 #公民教育 #政治教育<br />\n<br />\n[ 前途談判尾聲：議員倡政制比較，培育青年守護自由 ]<br />\n<br />\n話說1984年香港前途談判尾聲，港府提出代議政制改革，公民教育、政治教育突然受各方重視。被英方賞識的新任議員范徐麗泰，在立法局3月辯論「羅保動議」時借機談教育，主張專上學院要設立「政制比較」科推動參政意識，讓青年人選擇適當制度，又強調若無自由，香港繁榮亦將變成泡影。翌年教育署即推出公民教育指引，卻被批評以道德教育和社會控制淡化政治意識。<br />\n<br />\n范徐麗泰(1984)：<br />\n//&hellip;值此香港的政制可能會有所改變之際，香港人應該對世界各主要國家的政制有基本上的了解，來配合我們對香港社會運作的認識，以便日後能夠作出適合香港社會政制的建議&hellip;<br />\n眾所周知，我們最重要的目的，是保持現時大家所享有真正而不是紙上的自由&hellip;如果犧牲香港人的自由，則香港社會繁榮安定的目的，必難達到。//<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/huzsRkn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhuzsRkn.png&h=3f7744ac&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"337ffff81c63f5e64f6929583b583b0c706bf2b1","tid":2438815,"uid":103156,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T19:18:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qFG3pHi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqFG3pHi.jpg&h=966244e8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d45bbd0ecf11d9d32dcaaa7882b8770f27c5efa8","tid":2438815,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"337ffff81c63f5e64f6929583b583b0c706bf2b1","tid":2438815,"uid":103156,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T19:18:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qFG3pHi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqFG3pHi.jpg&h=966244e8&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T19:26:17.000Z","msg":"所以咪有紫荊黨 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33c9daa1f5df58ce3099a29beca190109f12ce2c","tid":2438815,"uid":149844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T19:46:37.000Z","msg":"勇士鬥惡龍<br />\n勇士變惡龍<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5552974a08ccfd30c616a754a20b6b57260c6459","tid":2438815,"uid":280593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T00:49:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"28fdef486634c38d42a6f7665da99693c9692f26","tid":2438815,"uid":10757,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T00:51:08.000Z","msg":"真心 有紫驚黨要佢留在度仲有咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}